 International sensation, Sam Smith has announced that he is bringing his Thrill of it AllÂ tour to South Africa in 2019. Fans of the soulful singer can catch him in Johannesburg on the 13th and 14th of April 2019 at the Ticketpro Dome. He will then move on to Cape Town for a performance at the Grand Arena, Grand West on the 16th and 17th of April 2019. Tickets for the concert will go on sale this Thursday, 30 August at 9am and are available from www.bigconcerts.co.za. Tickets for both cities will cost you R575.  